      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;About this site&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;about-this-site&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#about-this-site&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A long time ago, I wanted to find a place to write down my thoughts. First, it is convenient for me to look back and sigh at how I&amp;rsquo;ve grown. Second, my memory is not very good — after a while, I can&amp;rsquo;t remember how I dealt with a problem. Write it down, which is convenient for memory and reference. Third, some things are wrong paths I&amp;rsquo;ve taken — if writing them down can help others with the same problem, that&amp;rsquo;s a good thing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
